# Business Insights

## Project Title

**Strategic Product Placement Analysis Using Tableau**

---

# Introduction

Business insights are meaningful observations derived from data analysis that help organizations make informed decisions. Using Tableau dashboards, the retail dataset was analyzed to understand how product placement, customer demographics, pricing, discounts, and regional performance affect sales and revenue.

---

# Key Insights

## 1. Eye-Level Shelf Placement Generates Higher Sales

Products placed at **eye-level shelves** consistently recorded the highest number of units sold.

